Spartacus Educational Biography http://www.spartacus-educational.com/TUwheatley.htm On-line teaching aid by John Simkin&quot;John Wheatley&quot; by Ian Wood (Manchester University Press 1990)&quot;The Life of John Wheatley&quot; by John Hannan (Spokesman Books 1988)

===Fiction===
&quot;No Mean Affair&quot; by Robert Ronsson (Foxwell Press 2012)

